memberdef.name: dlist_for_each_safe
memberdef.initializer: for (pos = (head)->next, n = pos->next; pos != (head); \ pos = n, n = pos->next)

memberdef.name: dlist_for_each_entry
memberdef.initializer: for (node = aos_container_of((queue)->next, type, member); \ &node->member != (queue); \ node = aos_container_of(node->member.next, type, member))

memberdef.name: dlist_for_each_entry_safe
memberdef.initializer: for (node = aos_container_of((queue)->next, type, member), \ n = (queue)->next ? (queue)->next->next : NULL; \ &node->member != (queue); \ node = aos_container_of(n, type, member), n = n ? n->next : NULL)

memberdef.name: dlist_for_each_entry_reverse
memberdef.initializer: for (pos = list_entry((head)->prev, type, member); \ &pos->member != (head); \ pos = list_entry(pos->member.prev, type, member))

memberdef.name: slist_for_each_entry
memberdef.initializer: for (node = aos_container_of((queue)->next, type, member); \ &node->member; \ node = aos_container_of(node->member.next, type, member))

memberdef.name: slist_for_each_entry_safe
memberdef.initializer: for (node = aos_container_of((queue)->next, type, member), \ tmp = (queue)->next ? (queue)->next->next : NULL; \ &node->member; \ node = aos_container_of(tmp, type, member), tmp = tmp ? tmp->next : tmp)
